guides.name: Hans Mansson
guides.bio: Hans has an inborn love of nature and outdoors from his generations of family living on the river. His hobbies include: looking at the stars with his children, working out on a kayak daily (even on his days off) and a photography side hustle.

guides.name: Gina George
guides.bio: Gina was born in SLC but always wanted to live where she could be outdoors. Her hobbies include: cooking international foods, crocheting preemie baby hats, reading good detective mysteries and volunteering at a nursing home.

guides.name: Marc Parcher
guides.bio: Marc is a true Boy Scout: he is always prepared for anything. His hobbies include: taking classes whenever he can to learn new things, extreme mountain biking, and taking his child to the movies.
